OASISFormat: 0.4
Name:        transmission-rpc
Version:     1.0
Synopsis:    A client library for the Transmission Bittorrent client RPC
Authors:     Benoit Bataille <benoit.bataille@gmail.com>
Maintainers: Benoit Bataille <benoit.bataille@gmail.com>
License:     BSD-3-clause

Description: An OCaml client library for the Transmission Bittorrent client 
  RPC supporting all the available methods while remaining voluntarily close
  to the interface specification. To each specified method corresponds a 
  function which take advantages of some OCaml niceties: labelled arguments,
  optional arguments for optional parameters and variant types.
Homepage:    https://github.com/bataille/ocaml-transmission-rpc

Plugins:     META (0.4), DevFiles (0.4)
BuildTools:  ocamlbuild

Library transmission
  Path:         lib
  Pack:         true
  Findlibname:  transmission-rpc
  Modules:      Rpc, Client, Request, Answer
  BuildDepends:
    lwt,
    cohttp,
    cohttp.lwt,
    yojson,
    rresult,
    ppx_deriving.show,
    ppx_deriving_yojson
